= Listing Blocks

Listing blocks preserve text exactly as written, including whitespace and special characters.

== Basic Listing Block

----
This is a listing block.
It preserves all whitespace and formatting.
    Indentation is maintained.
----

== Listing Block with Code

----
#!/bin/bash
echo "Hello, World!"
cd /path/to/directory
ls -la
----

== Listing Block with Title

.Listing: Sample Configuration
----
database:
  host: localhost
  port: 5432
  name: myapp
----

== Listing Block with ID

[#config-listing]
.Listing: Environment Variables
----
NODE_ENV=production
API_KEY=secret123
DEBUG=false
----

== Multiple Listing Blocks

----
First listing block
----

----
Second listing block
with different content
----

== Listing Block with Special Characters

----
<tag>content</tag>
&entity;
"quoted text"
'single quotes'
----


